---
import SectionTitle from "./shared/SectionTitle.astro";
// import {Image} from "astro:assets"
import SWPCImage from "@assets/swpc.webp"
import ComicWikiImage from "@assets/comic-wiki.webp"
import WeddingInvitationImage from "@assets/wedding-invitation.webp"
import ButtonLink from "./shared/ButtonLink.astro";


---
<div class="flex-col space-y-10">
    <SectionTitle text="My Journey" />
    <p class="text-sm">
        I started in Industrial Engineering, which gave me a systems mindset, a grounding in statistics, and an instinct for optimisation. That foundation led me into software engineering and eventually into building AI-powered products. 
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm">
        I'm a Software Engineer at Quaisr in London, working across frontend and backend on an agentic AI product. Previously, I spent three years at LoveCare, a healthcare platform in Indonesia, where I built production features and explored how AI can improve healthcare workflows. I also hold an MSc in Data Science and AI with Distinction from the University of Liverpool.
    </p>
</div>
